data.value: Lucia Assorted Pastillas is a chewy milk candy is specially made from the finest ingredients of milk, sugar and flavorings of carrot, ube, buko-pandan, macapuno, and langka to make sure that it will be at its best flavor. Lucia Assorted Pastillas is wrapped individually in clear body bags to assure its freshness and quality taste.

data.name: Label50.Text
data.value: KSK Boy Bawang Garlic (Bawang) Cornick can satisfy any particular cravings that you might have. It is one of those corn snacks that does not have any extra-special ingredients. It was just perfectly deep-fried and made into light, crunchy corn bits. The simplicity of its flavor and taste makes it more appetizing and addicting.

data.name: Label44.Text
data.value: Fibisco Chocolate Crunchies are chocolate snacks loved by many through time because satisfaction granted in every delicious crunchy bite! Grab this crunchies in Just Asian Food and feel the goodness in every bite!

data.name: Label40.Text
data.value: Filipino meryenda will never be the same! Oishi Ribbed Cracklings in Salt and Vinegar flavor balances out the taste of salt and vinegar in pork rind snack that is light and fluffy yet crunchy, you will want to share it with your family and friends!

data.name: Label36.Text
data.value: Each bag of Jack n Jill Piattos is made specially with export quality potatoes and made to the highest quality standards. This crispy, cheesy and light tasting potato chips were designed to put a smile on everyone’s face, perfect for sharing with your friends, loved ones or even eat them alone. When you taste its rich flavor and feel its unique, and crispy thin texture, you'll know why there's no other snack like Piattos.

data.name: Label33.Text
data.value: The Sukang Paombong flavor of Chicharron Ni Mang Juan is a taste that Filipinos are very familiar of. This suka (vinegar) flavor originally came from a town called Paombong in the province of Bulacan in Luzon which became famous for its vinegar.

data.name: Label28.Text
data.value: Not only is this famous snack well known in the Philippines but Jack n' Jill Mr Chips Corn Chips Nacho Cheese Flavor is also an icon for corn chips lovers that look for that delicious nacho cheese in every crispy bite.

data.name: Label20.Text

data.name: Label12.Text
data.value: This Calbee Kettle Chips are orgin in japan that crafted kettle cooked potato chips that brings out the flavor of potato with a prefect crunch. Sodium content is 50% less than ordinary potato chips, allowing you to taste the real potato flavor.

data.name: Label8.Text
data.value: Lotte Crunky Crunch Chocolate is orgin in japan that a milk chocolate bar with tiny bits of crunchy malt puffs. This delicious crunchy bar is perfect for snacking and will definitely satisfy your chocolate cravings!

data.name: Label2.Text
